data.description: Welcome to this charming, single family home situated on just under 1 1/2 acres in the sought after Indian River Estates! This pool home boasts a gorgeous property with plenty of room for your boat, RV and other toys. With 4 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms plus a bonus room there is plenty of space for you and your family. A tropical Florida room leads you to a fenced in pool area that is ideal for entertaining. With your own finishing touches, this house could be your dream home!
